        "descriptions": [
          {
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "UBICOD Medivision Digital Signage 1.5.1 contains an authorization bypass vulnerability that allows normal users to escalate privileges by manipulating the 'ft[grp]' parameter. Attackers can send a GET request to /html/user with 'ft[grp]' set to integer value '3' to gain super admin rights without authentication."
